PermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/eid-al-fitr-in-the-shadow-of-war-palestinians-in-israel-mark-a-somber-holiday-celebration/0000018e-c730-dfe9-a19f-f77580fc0000</guid></item><item><title>拿撒勒家庭纠纷谋杀自杀案第四人受伤死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/fourth-person-dies-from-wounds-in-nazareth-family-dispute-murder-suicide/0000018e-c74b-dc93-adce-ef7bf58c0000</link><description>据邻居称，枪手今年 34 岁，因继承问题与母亲发生争执，被邻居视为问题人物。警方称枪手在杀死四名亲属并打伤两人后自杀</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 09:40:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/fourth-person-dies-from-wounds-in-nazareth-family-dispute-murder-suicide/0000018e-c74b-dc93-adce-ef7bf58c0000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其禁止对以色列关键出口是好的政治，坏的经济</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/turkeys-ban-on-key-exports-to-israel-is-good-politics-bad-economics/0000018e-c753-dfe9-a19f-f777709a0000</link><description>埃尔多安屈服于伊斯兰压力，以牺牲与以色列的贸易关系为代价，这对于陷入困境的土耳其经济来说是难得的一线曙光。但其他国家会效仿吗？</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 09:36:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/turkeys-ban-on-key-exports-to-israel-is-good-politics-bad-economics/0000018e-c753-dfe9-a19f-f777709a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列因对随机性的见解而获得计算机最高荣誉图灵奖</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-wins-turing-prize-computings-highest-honor-for-insights-on-randomness/0000018e-c735-dfe9-a19f-f77561e90000</link><description>计算机协会赞扬计算机科学家 Avi Wigderson 在创建能够描述我们混乱世界的计算机系统方面做出的贡献</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 09:06:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-wins-turing-prize-computings-highest-honor-for-insights-on-randomness/0000018e-c735-dfe9-a19f-f77561e90000</guid></item><item><title>“对我来说，活着就是节日的礼物”：战争中加沙的开斋节</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/for-me-staying-alive-is-the-holidays-gift-eid-al-fitr-in-gaza-amid-the-war/0000018e-c6ff-d1b7-a3af-e7ff8d4c0000</link><description>在大多数清真寺被毁、死亡气息无处不在的时候，加沙人不知道去哪里祈祷，也不知道是否应该祈祷。只有少数人能够摆摊出售节日用品，而有钱花的人就更少了。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 08:50:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/for-me-staying-alive-is-the-holidays-gift-eid-al-fitr-in-gaza-amid-the-war/0000018e-c6ff-d1b7-a3af-e7ff8d4c0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡对决策的厌恶阻碍了与哈马斯的人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/decision-averse-netanyahu-is-deliberately-holding-up-a-hamas-hostage-deal/0000018e-c480-d6f4-afaf-ecc286050000</link><description>哈马斯并不是开罗谈判中唯一拖延时间的一方。以色列总理似乎知道达成协议的代价可能是其联盟的终结，他与那些想要拒绝美国妥协的人站在一起，很可能将谈判引向死胡同</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 03:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/decision-averse-netanyahu-is-deliberately-holding-up-a-hamas-hostage-deal/0000018e-c480-d6f4-afaf-ecc286050000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高级部长考虑投票反对不包括所有人质的停火协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/top-israeli-ministers-will-vote-against-cease-fire-deal-that-does-not-include-all-hostages/0000018e-c4c5-dc93-adce-eef5e11b0000</link><description>内阁高级成员认为，这将是与哈马斯的最后一项以人质换取休战的协议，未来几轮谈判几乎是不可能的。据接近内塔尼亚胡的消息人士称，宗教犹太复国主义和奥兹玛·耶胡迪特部长将反对当前协议，但不会推翻联盟</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 03:00:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/top-israeli-ministers-will-vote-against-cease-fire-deal-that-does-not-include-all-hostages/0000018e-c4c5-dc93-adce-eef5e11b0000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨与内塔尼亚胡结盟，承诺以色列对拉法发动进攻，并返回汗尤尼斯身边</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article-live/biden-slams-netanyahus-handling-of-gaza-campaign-war-cabinet-discusses-truce-talks/0000018e-c5c4-dfe9-a19f-f5e59fb70000</link><description>英国首相称内塔尼亚胡必须采取更多措施来缓解加沙“难以忍受”的苦难 ■ 拜登在接受 Univision 采访时猛烈抨击内塔尼亚胡对加沙战争的处理方式：“他的做法是一个错误” ■ 被哈马斯扣押的美国人质的亲属会见了副总统哈里斯 ■ 以色列国防军表示，从汗尤尼斯撤军将有助于拉法的战斗</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 02:19:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article-live/biden-slams-netanyahus-handling-of-gaza-campaign-war-cabinet-discusses-truce-talks/0000018e-c5c4-dfe9-a19f-f5e59fb70000</guid></item><item><title>拜登猛烈抨击内塔尼亚胡处理加沙战争的方式：“他的做法是错误的”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/biden-slams-netanyahus-handling-of-gaza-war-what-hes-doing-is-a-mistake/0000018e-c507-d6f4-afaf-ed47502c0000</link><description>美国总统在就美国支持以色列战争努力发出迄今为止最明确的最后通牒一周后发表此番言论</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 22:56:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/biden-slams-netanyahus-handling-of-gaza-war-what-hes-doing-is-a-mistake/0000018e-c507-d6f4-afaf-ed47502c0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡浪费了以色列的国际信誉，现在他正在争取时间</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-frittered-away-israels-international-credit-and-now-hes-playing-for-time/0000018e-c4cc-dc93-adce-eefc6ef30000</link><description>由于以色列总理拒绝做出重大决定，只有他的联盟伙伴才能结束“比比时代”。是民族团结党领导的脱欧协议阵营，还是希望内塔尼亚胡向他们承诺的“全面胜利”的斯莫特里奇和本格维尔？</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 22:13:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-frittered-away-israels-international-credit-and-now-hes-playing-for-time/0000018e-c4cc-dc93-adce-eefc6ef30000</guid></item><item><title>针对俄亥俄州立大学未能解决犹太学生骚扰问题的投诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/complaint-filed-against-ohio-state-for-failing-to-address-harassment-of-jewish-students/0000018e-c4b1-dc93-adce-eef14d8e0000</link><descri